He looked to that weapon each and everyday.. and he knew the horrors which would come forth if he ever took upon that blade once again.<br>
But they did not scare him for his mind was already rend with power. With that weapon, he could become the strongest fighter on Norrath with Ease..<br>
He just had to learn how to use it with his Monken style of Fighting..<br>
<br>
So he took the sword each and every day he went out hunting beasts for meat, and more importantly..<br>
To gain in skill.<br>
<br>
But he had to be careful. The Guild of Monks would quickly disband him for using such a weapon, for the use of blades is outlawed.<br>
<br>
Because they feared what type of fighter would surface from such a style.<br>
Because they feared exactly what Ryo has become.<br>
<br>
His hunting trips did yield him skill and food, but it yielded him one more thing that he did not expect.<br>
His eyes watched the blood of his enemies splatter against the ground in crimson rains from each and every slice. His eyes.. they became darker and darker with each and every kill.<br>
<br>
His noble soul has faded. Now he was in the grip of something.<br>
Something evil.<br>
<br>
It did not take long for the Monks to find out that their brother, Ryo, had changed. His voice was no longer calm and quant. Such vile hatered becam seeping from this man that it could no longer be hidden.<br>
<br>
He was disbanded from the Monks. The soothing calm of Quellos has left his soul.<br>
<br>
He only wanted to do one thing now, Ryo did.<br>
He went out to fight with his sword.<br>
<br>
And he got himself into Several Fights.. on purpose.<br>
Using the aragonce of many to get them to challenge him on the battlefield, just so he could tear him apart with his sword. Ryo was an equal oppunity killer, any that wished to fight him could feel the taste of his Weapon, which he named simply..<br>
-Katana-<br>
<br>
And from every fight.. he could almost feel himself getting stronger, and stronger. .. And he looked down to the many that tryed to slay him..<br>
And he only had 6 words for them.<br>
<br>
&quot;You died because you are weak.&quot;<br>
<br>
Ryo continued like this for 2 years.. enought time to gain skill with his Katana, and be able to do what he wanted for those two years.<br>
<br>
Simple Revenge against the Monken Guild Leader, the one that threw him out of his guild so. Why kill him?<br>
To prove that his style was the best.<br>
<br>
And so.. he let his wish for Revenge dwell upon his mind..  Untill even Innoruuk's hate was allowed to touch him.<br>
.. And this is when he returned to the Monks, to fight them.<br>
<br>
